commit.message: Added additional licenses to `LICENSE` file, now allowing Apache 2.0 and MIT licensing.
Add support for custom attributes in form tags.

Fix pagination.html for Jinja2 v2.9.3.

Jinja2 2.9.3 made a change to the `with` block
source: https://github.com/pallets/jinja/blob/4e7fd1a521223c6627cfcd02db48a8e1765079ca/CHANGES#L41
that seems to have broken the pagination functionality.
